      "acceptanceCriteria": "Test conditions replicate intended use loading environment; multiple load levels or configurations evaluated.",
      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single load configuration (ASTM F1717 compression-bending at 10° offset) only. While the F1717 protocol is the regulatory standard, the single test condition limits confidence in model predictive capability across loading variations. Achieved level (2) is below required level (3); this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the regulatory precedent of F1717 as the sole required test configuration."
    },
